he's kind of busy, so I nominate Winged Warrior. 
Personally I hate taking other peoples chars, because
I don't pay enough attention to get their personality
right (not that anyone else does when they use chars
from the show, speaking of which Megatron should talk
to himself more, and just from watching the movie I
can determine Kup should use the word "lad" when
addressing Owlhawk, or Sunhawk).
